content: Look like a total badass by adorning your dapper suit with these stunning lighter cufflinks. These eye-catching little accessories look great on virtually any suit and are a great way to break the ice and spark up a conversation with a potential new flame.

Your lawn is the first line of defense from home intruders. Keep your home safe and sound with these combat lawn gnomes that are armed with AK-47s, rocket launchers, and grenades – those unwanted visitors won’t know what hit ’em!

Cuddle up with your furry friend anytime you want – even if you’re far away from them with your very own personalized dog pillow. Each comfy cushion is emblazoned with a cartoon styled portrait of your beloved companion so he’ll always be by your side.

titleEN: Miniature Fairy Door And Ladder Set
content: Create a magical and whimsical atmosphere for your little princess by decorating her room with this cute little miniature fairy door and ladder set. This set helps you create the illusion that there are small fairies living inside the walls of your humble abode.

If industrial-looking flash drives aren’t really your style, these lovely crystal glass USB flash drives will be perfect for you. They’re available in either 8, 16, or 32 GB models and are complemented with an elegant crystal body.

This rolling dice tower will turn the mundane task of rolling the die into the most fun part of your next D&D game night. It comes with a removable catch tray and can be delivered un-assembled upon request so that you can give the tower a custom paint job!

If you need a little relaxing ambient lighting for your next seance, this large skull shaped candle is exactly what you’re looking for. Each candle is handmade using natural dyes and fragrant oils and will burn for anywhere from 10 to 15 hours.

These mustard and ketchup baby costumes will transform your little bundles of joy into the most iconic duo of the condiment world. These adorable onesies are available for babies from 3 to 18 months old and will be a sure fire hit for either Halloween or your next BBQ.

Instantly go from plain Jane to tattooed badass by decorating your skin with one or two of these skull hand temporary tattoos. Each tattoo is handmade from non-toxic ingredients and will last anywhere from three to five days.

Make your mundane bathroom trips more exciting and macabre by washing yourself with these Ouija board themed soap bars. The set comes with one bar shaped like a tiny Ouija board while the other is styled like the accompanying planchette.

titleEN: Kratos God Of War Cosplay Costume
content: Strike fear into the hearts of others by transforming yourself into the Ghost of Sparta with this Kratos cosplay costume. This expertly handmade costume includes everything from a leather pauldron to shin guards and is tailored to your exact measurements.

Ensure your rally is a huge tremendous success by filling the air with these incredible baby Trump party balloons. These presidential party props will incite laughter and draw record breaking crowds so big that no one will believe you.

titleEN: Evil Demon Baby Belly Halloween Prop
content: Get your unborn fetus in on all the Halloween fun by transforming your angelic baby bump into an evil demon using this custom baby belly prop. Simply wear the prop with a tight shirt to create the illusion that Satan’s spawn is trying to bust out of your belly.

Liven up the mundane task of flipping a switch by turning your lights on and off with this steampunk light switch. With this light switch cover, every time you want the lights on or off you’ll have to grab onto an old-timey lever and move your entire hand up or down.

Instantly liven up any dull bathroom with a few of these incredibly vibrant rainbow crystal soaps. These custom handmade soap bars sport an eye-catching multicolored motif and feature a sweet and fruity tangerine scent that will leave you smelling springtime fresh.

Give guests fair warning to the chaos that awaits them inside your clusterf*ck of a home with this “welcome to the shitshow” doormat. This 30 x 18 inch mat is handmade from 100% choir and industrial outdoor paint made to withstand the elements.

If you love geek culture, you have to check out the amazing hand made wooden scultpures from Etsy shop Love My Custom Wooden. You’ll find stunning and intricately detailed sculptures depicting everyone from Venom to the Millennium Falcon.

Ensure all eyes are on you this Halloween by transforming yourself into Tekashi 6ix9ine using these temporary face tattoos. The set includes all the dope facial ink you’ll need to look like the inexplicably famous soundcloud “rapper”.

Transform yourself into the stuff of nightmares by slipping into this terrifying Babadook costume and hitting the streets. This bone-chilling ensemble is handmade and includes a weathered top hat, latex mask with dreadlocked hair, and an oversized black coat.

Take part in one of the most famous thought experiments of all time by ordering your very own Schrodinger’s cat in a box. You can either request a “dead” or an “alive” cat pin or leave it up to chance and see which one you get upon opening the box, or not.

Strike terror into the hearts of trick-or-treaters everywhere by walking the streets in your very own 4-legged Stilt Spirit costume. This premium tutorial will provide you with helpful instructions so that you can make your own terrifying ensemble at home.

Get your kids excited about eating their veggies by treating them to these delectable chocolate Brussels sprouts. They’re handmade from rich white chocolate and come in packs of 8 green little sprouts that will send your taste buds into ecstasy.

Create a fun and safe environment for the little monsters to play in with help from the modern smart playhouse. Unlike the tree houses of yesteryear, these homes are as easy to assemble as Ikea furniture and feature an insulated roof to prevent over heating.

This human hedge costume is perfect for scaring unsuspecting trick-or-treaters half to death when they venture onto your property. It’s custom made from green plastic foliage that give this quirky ensemble a frightfully realistic appearance.

Make bathtime a little more magical by lathering up with these colorful unicorn soap bars. These eye-catching handmade bars feature a delightful melon ball scent and a vibrant rainbow design that is topped off with a lovely golden unicorn horn.

When hunger strikes, nothing hits the spot quite like a fresh out-of-the-oven people pot pie. Upon slicing through the deliciously flaky face crust, you’re treated to a 9″ deep smorgasbord of savory bits that goes great with some fava beans and a nice Chianti.

Fend off the cold in true Jedi fashion by keeping your Force-sensitive member snug and comfy in this eye-catching lightsaber willy warmer. Each of these geeky peter heaters will transform your twig and berries into a mighty and deadly lightsaber.

Help the over-worked and over-stressed med student in your life relax a little by surprising them with this anatomically correct heart bath bomb. Upon being dropped into a warm tub, the heart begins to dissolve and release a blend of soothing oils and fragrances.

Help keep strangers off your perfectly manicured lawn by unleashing these horror movie garden gnomes. If these ghoulish garden gnomes look a bit familiar, it’s because they’re designed like the most terrifying and iconic movie monsters in cinematic history.

Take teatime on the road by carrying your teacup and accompanying saucer in this distinguished steampunk teacup leather holster. The holster will securely hold your porcelain or glass teacup so that you can enjoy your tea wherever you like.

Nothing sets the mood for a romantic candle-lit evening quite like lighting up this bleeding hand candle. This morbid wax candle features a layered design that creates the effect of a human hand melting right down to the bone from the heat of the flames.

Pay homage to your favorite childhood Halloween flick with this Hocus Pocus Sanderson sisters doormat. Each 30″ x 18″ doormat features a creative minimalist rendition of the 3 wicked Sanderson sisters plus their classic “I smell children” line.

Nothing bonds people quite like constantly gossiping about others when they’re not around. This hilarious “I love talking sh*t” card is the perfect way to tell your gossipy and wonderful bff, coworker, sarcastic friend, or favorite sibling how much they mean to you.

Uncover the treasures Mother Nature hides right in front of our eyes by breaking apart these geodes. Although they appear like run-of-the-mill stones at first sight, once you break them open you’ll uncover dozens of glimmering crystals that line the inner walls.

Keep your skin looking as radiant as ever by making this organic coffee scrub part of your daily beauty routine. Each 4-ounce jar is filled with a specially formulated organic coffee sugar scrub designed to gently rub away dead skin cells while drawing moisture to your skin.

This All Hallows Eve, stand out from every other witch in town by giving your getup a unique and whimsical twist with this Halloween witch hat. Each hat is skillfully handmade to your exact measurements and can be customized with the brim length of your choice.

Drop this witch’s cauldron bath bomb in your warm tub and watch it transform into a soothing potion of relaxation and delight. Each bomb is made with pure high quality essential oils like sunflower seed and other fragrance oils.

titleEN: My Love Is Like A Candle
content: Let your significant other know how hot your fiery passion for them burns by gifting them this “My love is like a candle” custom candle. This pure soy wax candle is available in sizes ranging from a 4 ounce jar to a massive 26 ounce jar with a 200+ hour burn time.

titleEN: I Have To Go Poop Now Coffee Mug
content: Avoid making small-talk with coworkers while you sip your hot roast by serving it in this “I have to go poop now” coffee mug. This ceramic mug comes printed with a comical chart that indicates at what point in your drink others may speak to you.

Do your gender reveal celebration the right way by making the announcement using this explosive gender reveal confetti cannon. This small confetti popper is able to blast confetti up to 30ft in the air, making it perfect for either indoor or outdoor use.

Make showers more fun and magical for the little heck-raisers by installing this rainbow unicorn head showerhead in bathroom. This custom made piece will rejuvenate you with the magical and healing properties of high velocity unicorn discharge.

Make your Cloud Strife cosplay look more authentic than ever by complementing it with this Final Fantasy Buster Sword. With this digital file download, you’ll be able to make your very own Buster Sword for a truly one-of-a-kind look and feel.

Life is hard. Help keep your sanity by keeping your stress levels low with this “calm the f**ck down” candle. This vegan-friendly custom soy wax candle comes in an elegant little glass jar and is made with a mixture of soothing ingredients like lavender and chamomile.

Turn your next soak into a total bloodbath by dropping in this great white shark bath bomb. Once you drop this ravenous great white into your warm tub waters, the shark dissolves, turning the water red and unleashing a tropical fruity scent.

This stunning smart LED fur coat is the understated classic that rivals the little black dress in terms of versatility for all social settings. No matter what the occasion, this saucy little number will turn heads and make you shine brighter than anyone in the room.

Marshmallows aren’t just for kids – feast your eyes on these gourmet marshmallows! These delectable treats put a new spin on an old classic. With 13 unique flavors that’ll tantalize your taste buds with every bite, these gourmet treats are ideal for any occasion.

Keep your energetic kid entertained by promoting a healthy lifestyle with the climbing box. It features a 45 degree angled 118″ wall with over 500 nuts installed so that you can simulate various types of holds in addition to a 24″ roof that lets you mount extra add-ons.

Spice up your kitchen’s decor by covering the walls with this Mexican Talavera tile decal. Made from vinyl, they can be easily placed onto the walls and are decorated with 22 different colorful designs based on the famous Talavera tiles from Puebla, Mexico.

titleEN: Aqua Teen Hunger Force Carl Statue
content: Everyone’s favorite porn-loving loud-mouthed sports fan is here to class up your desktop! This pint-sized Aqua Teen Hunger Force Carl statue comes dressed in his signature wifebeater and features a hyper-realistic appearance complete with real human hair.

Add some charm to your lifeless workstation by switching on this industrial robot pipe lamp. This helpful little guy not only provides quaint ambient lighting, but also provides you with a handy place to rest your smartphone while it charges.

Instantly add depth, texture, and a whole lot of style to any room in your humble abode with this imposing speaker wall mural. This HD woven paper and vinyl decal can be easily applied to any flat surface and is waterproof. It’s the perfect gift for any audiophile.

Put your self control to the ultimate test by playing with this dessert scented slime without trying to take a big old bite out of it. Available in either a 4, 6, or 8 ounce size, each flavor features an mouth-watering scent and looks good enough to eat… but don’t!

Marvel at the molecular complexity of your favorite beverage by sipping your frosty brew from this beer chemistry glass. This neat 16 ounce glass displays the complex array of molecules such as humulene and ethanol that make up this heavenly nectar.

Break away from the traditional while still conforming to the traditional by sealing the deal with these cyberpunk wedding rings. These futuristic styled rings are skillfully crafted from premium .925 sterling silver and are handmade to order.

Now you can enjoy farm fresh eggs on the daily by building your own chicken coop in your backyard. With this purchasable PDF as your guide, you’ll be able to construct a quaint rectangular walk-in coop that is large enough to house up to 16 chickens.

Fool onlookers into thinking you have other-worldy superhuman powers using this floating fireball prop. It features a transparent plastic base that goes around your hand to create the illusion you’ve got a glowing fireball hovering just inches above your palm.

Give your formal wear a sinister and distinguished flair by heading out of your house with this skull walking cane. This stunning cane sports a black shaft composed of solid ash wood that is complemented by a menacing sterling silver coated skull on top.

What better way to add color and warmth to your home than with one of these visually striking rainbow drip candles?! Each custom candle is skillfully crafted from paraffin wax with a cotton wick and will burn for roughly four hours.

Pay homage to your favorite Game Of Thrones character next time you wet your whistle by pouring your Scotch in this distinguished whiskey glass. This 8 oz. glass comes etched with the now infamous line uttered by Tyrion Lannister regarding his knowledge of dragons.

Transform yourself into an adorable woodland critter by keeping warm inside this kawaii fox hoodie. Made of ginger and black cotton knitwear, this cute little garment features an over sized hood complemented by a pair of cute little fox ears.

Send shivers running down the spines of everyone at Comic-Con by showing up in this insane Alien cosplay costume. This incredibly detailed getup is entirely handmade and painted to ensure a high level of detail and includes a head, torso, arms, legs, feet, and a tail.

Ensure you always have a little something to wet you whistle with when you require a little social lubrication by attaching this leather flask to your keychain. Each pint-sized one ounce flask holds one shot’s worth of your favorite poison so it’s always handy.

This stunning steampunk nixie clock will ensure you always have something to talk about when guests pop by for a visit. This two-in-one device comes fitted with a handy clock along with a built-in telegraph sounder that actually works!

You can now own one of the best things to find in Fornite! This colorful little 3D printed Fortnight llama coin bank measures eight inches long, stands at 10.5 inches tall, and makes a great and useful little gift that the Fornite crazed gamer in your life will surely love.

What better way to surprise your firearm loving significant other on their special day than with these gun and grenade shaped soap bars? They’re made from soothing ingredients like almond oil, vitamin E, and other essential skin alleviating ingredients.

Give your reptilian friend a little gamer-inspired flair by slipping him into this crochet Bowser turtle shell. This geeky custom piece is handmade from yarn to ensure a perfect fit and comes accented with giant white spikes that will make him look more fearsome than ever.

Become the living embodiment of everyone’s favorite Guardian of the Galaxy by dressing up in this impressive full body Groot costume. This elaborate getup covers you from head to toe and is handmade to ensure a perfect fit.

This hummingbird feeder gives you a front row seat to the all the action. One end of this custom copper feeder features a paperclip-like design that allows you to conveniently attach it to the front of your cap so that you can get an up close view of the birdy while he feeds.

Live a more stress-free life by taking a cue from The Dude and learning to let go of everyday worries. With this kit you’ll be able to build your very own 1:6 scale urethane model of The Dude abiding – complete with a bowling ball, white Russian, and a joint in hand.

You wouldn’t usually think of a cactus as your go-to snuggle buddy, but these cactus pillows will change everything! These cuddly cacti are handmade using soft green fleece and are filled with a super plush fiberfill perfect for laying down on.

Make your outfit sizzle and your mouth drool with these pepperoni pizza socks. These unisex high socks are covered with a bold and mouth-watering graphic designed to make your legs look like two tasty slices of pepperoni pizza.

titleEN: I’d Burn This Place Down Candle
content: Show your favorite cubicle mate how much they mean to you by surprising them this “I’d burn this place down” candle. Handmade and customized with the scent of your choice, this 8 ounce soy wax candle features a 45-55 hour burn time and comes in a quaint little mason jar.

Make your bedroom the most exotic part of your home with this incredible 3d waterfall steps floor mural decal. This 100% German heavy duty vinyl creates the illusion your bedroom is smack in the middle of a quaint little stone pond.

Add some wonder and whimsy to your yard’s night time ambiance using this lovely fairy light waterfall watering can. This custom lighting fixture creates the illusion you’re watering your lively garden with streams of magical fairy light.

Make your toilet bowl great again by keeping it spick and span with this Trump toilet brush. Forty-five won’t disappoint as he puts his glorious golden faux-locks to work to drain that porcelain swamp. Your toilet is going to look so good folks, believe me.

Really get into character the next time you head into virtual battle by wearing this Call of Duty Ghost mask. Expertly crafted from fiberglass, it’s masterfully painted by hand and topped off with a gelcoat layer for added strength and durability.

titleEN: I Survived Another Meeting Coffee Mug
content: Make your displeasure for meetings known to everyone at the office by sipping your brew from this “I survived another meeting that should have been an e-mail” coffee mug. It’s the perfect way for disgruntled employees to voice their discontent in a passive-aggressive way.

Who says you have to spend a fortune to create an awesome costume your kid will love? This pdf will provide you with step-by-step illustrated instructions that will show you how to craft a cool retro robot costume out of everyday items you can find lying around the home.

Give your home some old world charm by flicking on this giant LED Edison bulb. This massive 220 volt bulb is a sure-fire conversation piece that measures almost 1 foot long and has a lifespan of around 3,000 hours – making this a great addition of any room in your home.

Trick guests into playing the circle game by placing this eye-catching sequin pillow in your living room. Upon running your hand down the pillow’s surface, the red sequin magically disappears to reveal an image of hand creating a circle with its thumb and index finger.

Bring your favorite fighting-type Pokemon to life by topping off your Pokemon cosplay using this custom Machoke mask. The mask is skillfully handmade from a combination of polyurethane resin and latex for a more comfortable fit.

This one-of-a-kind handmade nixie tube chessboard is sure to make your next match more exciting than ever. Instead of traditional pieces, this fully assembled custom chessboard comes with a set of round IN-7 nixie pieces complemented by brass fittings.

titleEN: Game Of Thrones Hold The Door Doormat
content: Hold the door! Hold the door! Hold the door! Hold the door! Hold the door! Hold the door! Hold the door! Hold the door! Hold the dor! Hold the dor! Hold the dor! Hol de dor! Hol de dor! Hol de dor! Holdor! Holdor! Hodor! Hodor! Hodor… Hodor…

Spice up your look with some bohemian flair by slipping into these red rose tattoo pantyhose. These unique tights feature a lovely hand painted red rose that creates the illusion your virgin legs are all tatted up with eye-catching massive floral tattoos.

Pledge your life long service and loyalty to the ruler who sits on the Iron Throne when you gear up from head to toe in this authentic and fully functional Game of Thrones inspired Kingsguard armor. Unless Joffrey is king. Eff that guy.

Defend your castle like a true Samurai when you arm your household with one of these authentic Wakizashi swords. This handmade sword is forged from spring steel, hardened for added durability, and sharpened to a razor sharp edge.

titleEN: Game Of Thrones Baby Dragon Sculpture
content: Become the Mother of Dragons by adding this incredibly lifelike Game of Thrones baby dragon sculpture to your collection. This beautifully sculpted polyurethane resin dragon measures 21 inches wide, 13 inches deep, and stands at 11.5 inches tall.

Kill the fashion game by topping off your trendy outfit with these impossible-to-miss personalized face socks. These custom printed nylon and polyester socks come with the face of your choosing plastered over every square inch of these fashionable accessories.

Give your furry friend some added allure by transforming them into a lovable Pokemon by purchasing a personalized pet card. Each handmade card comes with a cartoon image of your pet along with details like HP, Pokemon type, and attack moves.

Pay tribute to your favorite dino blockbuster of all time by adding this Jurassic Park raptor claw replica to your collection. This awesome acrylic, urethane, resin, and plastic prop has been expertly handmade to resemble the giant claw Dr. Alan Grant carried in the iconic film.

Get your best buddy’s special night started off right by giving him the shot glass birthday card. The unique design of this novelty card allows your friend to cut out and fold the card into a small paper shot glass they can actually use for birthday shots.

Let anyone who enters your home know where your allegiances lie by proudly having this DIY papercraft Darth Vader statue on display. By following the instructions of this PDF you’ll be able to construct a cool 3D bust of the sinister Lord Vader.

Bring your Han Solo cosplay to life by topping it off with this hyper realistic blaster prop. Modeled after Han’s iconic blaster, this hand painted 3D printed prop features movie-accurate detailing and measures roughly 11 inches long.

Break away from tradition and make a bold fashion statement by trading in your standard band for this rustic men’s wedding ring. This eye-catching piece sports a dark copper band at the center and is lined by two contrasting sterling silver edges.

Turn yourself into a walking art exhibit by heading out of the house in this stunning Starry Night skirt. This handmade garment depicts the late post impressionist’s most iconic masterpiece in stunning color that is guaranteed to turn heads.

Make the most out of your discarded bottle caps by using them to play on this magnetic bottle opener plinko board. It comes fitted with a sturdy bottle opener at the top and small magnets at the bottom that are designed to keep your bottle cap from falling onto the floor.

Let your little one’s imagination soar by turning them into a superhero with one of these personalized capes. Each wearable cape is made upon request and can be fitted with a specific letter/logo and color scheme to match your child’s inner super hero identity.

Take Comic-Con by storm by showing up in this incredible Fallout 4 T60 power armor. This eye-catching getup is hand made from a combination of PVC plastic and resin to your specific measurements to ensure a perfect fit.

Take your party to another dimension by creating amazing visuals with help from this tesseract hypercube. This stunning and psychedelic piece depicts one artist’s interpretation of a 4-dimensional cube commonly known as a tesseract.

Why slice through a boring old cake when you can reveal your future baby’s gender by smashing one of these baseballs?! When you hit the ball it will burst open and release the pink or blue powder into the air in one colorful explosion that is guaranteed to wow.
